<p source="SHANGBO.WANGJU-ZHISHU 8.48-8.49.1 (STRIPS WJ1, NY1) MACHENGYUAN 8: 206, 218 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-1a.1">王居{於}蘇澫之室.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-1a.2">彭徒返陽關致命,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-1a.3">郘昌爲之告.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-1a.4">王未答之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-1a.5">觀無畏】（WJ1）持書乃言.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-1a.6">是楚邦之強梁人.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-1a.7">反側其口舌</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-1a.8">以變譌[化]王.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.WANGJU-ZHISHU 8.48-8.49.2 (STRIPS NY1-NY2) MACHENGYUAN 8: 218-219 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-2a.1">大夫之言,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-2a.2">縦 】（NY１）不獲罪,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-2a.3">或猶走[還]趨事王,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-2a.4">邦人其謂之何.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.WANGJU-ZHISHU 8.48-8.49.4 (STRIPS M4, M5, NY5, NY4, NY6) MACHENGYUAN 8: 195-196, 222, 221, 223 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-3a.1">吾聞古】（M４）之善臣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-3a.2">不以私惠私怨入于王門.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-3a.3">非而[=爾]所以復我.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-3a.4">不能貫壁而視聽】（M５）</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-3a.5">吾以爾爲遠目耳.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-3a.6">而縱不爲吾稱,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-3a.7">擇吾父兄甥舅之有所善，（NY５）</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-3a.8">蟲(=昆=掄) [蟲*d-lung=庸*long]材以爲獻，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-3a.9">又不能節處所以罪人，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-3a.10">然以讒言相謗.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-3a.11">爾使我】（NY４）得尤於邦多已.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-3a.12">吾欲致爾於罪.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.WANGJU-ZHISHU 8.48-8.49.5 (STRIPS NY6, NY7, WJ5) MACHENGYUAN 8: 223, 224, 210 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-4a.1">邦人其謂</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-4a.2">我不能稱人.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-4a.3">朝起而】（NY６）夕廢之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-4a.4">是則盡不穀之罪也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-4a.5">後余勿然.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-4a.6">雖我愛爾,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-4a.7">吾無如社）】（NY７） 稷何.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-4a.8">而[爾]必良愼之.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.WANGJU-ZHISHU 8.48-8.49.6 (STRIPS WJ5, WJ6) MACHENGYUAN 8: 210-211 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-5a.1">其明日令尹子春厭[狎].</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-5a.2">王就之曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-5a.3">夫彭徒一勞爲】（王居５）吾</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-5a.4">蔽之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-5a.5">令尹答</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-5a.6">命須其儘.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-5a.7">王謂:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-5a.8">吾欲速.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-5a.9">乃許諾,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-5a.10">命須後蔽.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.WANGJU-ZHISHU 8.48-8.49.7 (STRIPS WJ6, WJ3, WJ4) MACHENGYUAN 8: 211, 209 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-6a.1">王就）】（王居６）之曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-6a.2">無畏墮惡之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-6a.3">是言旣聞於衆已.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-6a.4">邦人其沮志解體</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-6a.5">謂）［不能稱］.】（王居３）</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-6a.6">［彭徒］一能進後人.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-6a.7">願大夫之毋背.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0077_tls_001-6a.8">徒以損不穀之尤.】（王居４）</seg>
                </p>

</div>
